Package org.eclipse.jetty.annotations

Class AnnotationConfiguration.ServletContainerInitializerOrdering

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jetty.annotations.AnnotationConfiguration.ServletContainerInitializerOrdering
  • Enclosing class:
    AnnotationConfiguration

    public class AnnotationConfiguration.ServletContainerInitializerOrdering
extends java.lang.Object
    ServletContainerInitializerOrdering A list of classnames of ServletContainerInitializers in the order in which they are to be called back. One name only in the list can be "*", which is a wildcard which matches any other ServletContainerInitializer name not already matched.
